Machine-independent code for multiprocessing support.

Machine-dependent stuff appears to live in:

    src/runtime/mp

As of 2007, apparently unused for years, and never implemented
on x86 anyhow (only SGI &tc).

See:

     A Portable Multiprocessor Interface for SML/NJ
     J Gregor Morrisett (CMU), Andrew Tolmach (Princeton)
     1992, 31p
     http://www.cs.cornell.edu/home/jgm/papers/jgmorris-mp.ps 


